Class ProjectFile

java.lang.Object
DataItems.ProjectFile
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable
public class ProjectFile extends Object implements Serializable
This is intended to hold all of the data used in a project. User-input data, settings, all of that.

The Model in the MVC pattern.

Author:
Victor Malone
